description:
• Collaborating with team members to design, develop and deliver user-friendly mobile applications with Flutter.
  • Implementing custom features and functionalities based on client requirements.

• Evaluate candidates' responses for adherence to best engineering practices in a variety of technical assessments.
  • Review and hand results to the clients (hiring managers at tech companies).
  • Assessments include coding challenges, collaboration scenarios (emails, customer support tickets), system design, and other formats.
